  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd9\u0da9 \u0d87\u0db3\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Samanpriya Herat comes from sick bed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Podujana Peramuna's Kurunegala District Member Mr. Saman Priya Herath, who is seriously ill, came to Parliament and cast his vote.",
        "The saline bottle was also attached to his body and he was seen voting with great difficulty.",
        "With the permission of the House, the Secretary General of the Parliament gave him the opportunity to vote without standing until his name was called."
      ],
